summary.label:
This is an easy educational game for children from three years old. It does not load the child's brain with unorganized information. This game is a training of all higher mental functions: attention, memory, thinking and speech.
In this game, the child needs to save Christmas: find Santa Claus, dress up the Christmas tree, fix the garland, find the attributes of the Santa Claus costume and pick up gifts for the children.
The game is developed according to the methodology of a professional neuropsychologist and speech therapist. The game follows the principle of "from simple to complex", which makes its passage fascinating and helps to stimulate mental activity. The following instructions for parents are attached to the game:
- play the game together with the child: ask the child leading questions;
- if required, show a reasoning model when playing the game;
- take breaks, don't try to go through the whole game at once;
- after completing the game completely, do not rush to delete it, go through it again, because it is useful for the development of memory;
- start the game with a good mood, it will increase the efficiency of assimilation of information.
